com.github.jsontemplate.valueproducer

类 SmartValueProducer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jsontemplate.valueproducer.AbstractValueProducer<JsonNode>
      • com.github.jsontemplate.valueproducer.SmartValueProducer
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    IValueProducer<JsonNode>

    public class SmartValueProducer
extends AbstractValueProducer<JsonNode>
    This is the default type in JsonTemplate. It produces a value with the type which the value looks like. For example:
    • "null" results in null
    • "true" results in true
    • "fAlSe" results in false
    • "1" results in 1
    • "1f" results in 1.0
    • "hello" results in "hello"

    The smart type is designed to be used only for the fixed value. For example:
    {name : @smart(John)} will result in {name : John}
    However,
    {name : @smart} will result in {name : null}
